EventDescription: A unique opportunity to speak at an event to a group of passionate, ambitious and dedicated Developers. You have the chance to increase your knowledge.
LeadDescription: Developer Student Club Leads are passionate leaders at their university who are dedicated to helping their peers learn and connect. These Leads have a good foundational knowledge of software development concepts.Google collaborates with DSC Leads once a year who are pursuing an undergraduate or graduate university degree and supports them as they start and grow their on-campus community.
